00:02:56.880 --> 00:03:01.379
Lester, who has been using the portal in order
to live longer, reveals his plan to use Malkovich

00:03:01.379 --> 00:03:06.180
when "ripe" as the host for him and several
of his elderly friends. Offered the chance

00:03:06.180 --> 00:03:11.170
to join Lester's group, Lotte warns him that
Craig currently has control of Malkovich.

00:03:11.170 --> 00:03:15.859
Craig finds he is able to remain in Malkovich
permanently. He spends the next eight months

00:03:15.859 --> 00:03:19.959
in Malkovich's body, using his skills as a
‘puppeteer’, he is able to turn Malkovich

00:03:19.959 --> 00:03:25.440
into a world-class puppeteer as narrated
over a TV special. Malkovich marries Maxine.

00:03:25.440 --> 00:03:28.999
He learns that she is pregnant though their
relationship grows distant.

00:03:28.999 --> 00:03:33.719
As Malkovich's 44th birthday approaches, Lester
and his friends make a deal with Maxine, and

00:03:33.719 --> 00:03:38.999
fake her kidnapping. They call up Craig, threatening
to kill her if Craig does not leave Malkovich.

00:03:38.999 --> 00:03:43.250
Craig ends the call, causing Lester to think
that he is calling their bluff. Lotte loses

00:03:43.250 --> 00:03:47.139
hope and tries to kill Maxine, but they end
up at the turnpike after falling through the

00:03:47.139 --> 00:03:51.950
portal and through Malkovich's shame-ridden
subconscious. Maxine reveals to Lotte that

00:03:51.950 --> 00:03:56.640
Maxine conceived when Lotte was inside Malkovich's
body, and she kept the child because it is

00:03:56.640 --> 00:03:57.360
"theirs".

00:03:57.360 --> 00:03:59.660
This reveal cements their love
for each other.

00:03:59.740 --> 00:04:04.579
Craig calls back Lester, thinking Maxine is
still in danger. Realizing his opportunity,

00:04:04.579 --> 00:04:09.739
Lester continues his bluff, convincing Craig
to leave Malkovich's body which he does

00:04:09.740 --> 00:04:12.700
Lester and his friends enter the portal ,taking control of Malkovich.

00:04:12.700 --> 00:04:14.420
Craig, discovering that Lotte and

00:04:14.420 --> 00:04:18.130
Maxine are together again, decides to enter
the portal to become Malkovich and regain

00:04:18.130 --> 00:04:21.500
Maxine’s love, however he
has unknowingly missed the deadline for getting

00:04:21.500 --> 00:04:26.041
into Malkovich. Years later, an aging Malkovich,
containing the collective mind of Lester and

00:04:26.041 --> 00:04:30.130
his friends, reveals to Charlie Sheen a plan
to prolong their lives via Maxine's daughter

00:04:30.130 --> 00:04:35.030
Emily, within whom Craig is now permanently
trapped. Through Emily's eyes Craig watches

00:04:35.030 --> 00:04:37.780
Maxine and Lotte living happily together.

